{"ja510:0.1":"Jataka ","ja510:0.2":"Visatinipata ","ja510:0.3":"Matangavagga ","ja510:0.4":"14. Ayogharajataka ","ja510:1.1":"“Yamekarattim pathamam, ","ja510:1.2":"gabbhe vasati manavo; ","ja510:1.3":"Abbhutthitova so yati, ","ja510:1.4":"sagaccham na nivattati. ","ja510:2.1":"Na yujjhamana na balenavassita, ","ja510:2.2":"Nara na jiranti na capi miyyare; ","ja510:2.3":"Sabbam hidam jatijarayupaddutam, ","ja510:2.4":"Tam me mati hoti carami dhammam. ","ja510:3.1":"Caturanginim senam subhimsarupam, ","ja510:3.2":"Jayanti ratthadhipati pasayha; ","ja510:3.3":"Na maccuno jayitumussahanti, ","ja510:3.4":"Tam me mati hoti carami dhammam. ","ja510:4.1":"Hatthihi assehi rathehi pattibhi, ","ja510:4.2":"Parivarita muccare ekacceyya; ","ja510:4.3":"Na maccuno muccitumussahanti, ","ja510:4.4":"Tam me mati hoti carami dhammam. ","ja510:5.1":"Hatthihi assehi rathehi pattibhi, ","ja510:5.2":"Sura pabhanjanti padhamsayanti; ","ja510:5.3":"Na maccuno bhanjitumussahanti, ","ja510:5.4":"Tam me mati hoti carami dhammam. ","ja510:6.1":"Matta gaja bhinnagala pabhinna, ","ja510:6.2":"Nagarani maddanti janam hananti; ","ja510:6.3":"Na maccuno madditumussahanti, ","ja510:6.4":"Tam me mati hoti carami dhammam. ","ja510:7.1":"Issasino katahatthapi vira, ","ja510:7.2":"Durepati akkhanavedhinopi; ","ja510:7.3":"Na maccuno vijjhitumussahanti, ","ja510:7.4":"Tam me mati hoti carami dhammam. ","ja510:8.1":"Sarani khiyanti saselakanana, ","ja510:8.2":"Sabbam hidam khiyati dighamantaram; ","ja510:8.3":"Sabbam hidam bhanjare kalapariyayam, ","ja510:8.4":"Tam me mati hoti carami dhammam. ","ja510:9.1":"Sabbesa mevam hi narana narinam, ","ja510:9.2":"Calacalam panabhunodha jivitam; ","ja510:9.3":"Patova dhuttassa dumova kulajo, ","ja510:9.4":"Tam me mati hoti carami dhammam. ","ja510:10.1":"Dumapphalaneva patanti manava, ","ja510:10.2":"Dahara ca vuddha ca sarirabheda; ","ja510:10.3":"Nariyo nara majjhimaporisa ca, ","ja510:10.4":"Tam me mati hoti carami dhammam. ","ja510:11.1":"Nayam vayo tarakarajasannibho, ","ja510:11.2":"Yadabbhatitam gatameva dani tam; ","ja510:11.3":"Jinnassa hi natthi rati kuto sukham, ","ja510:11.4":"Tam me mati hoti carami dhammam. ","ja510:12.1":"Yakkha pisaca athavapi peta, ","ja510:12.2":"Kupita te assasanti manusse; ","ja510:12.3":"Na maccuno assasitussahanti, ","ja510:12.4":"Tam me mati hoti carami dhammam. ","ja510:13.1":"Yakkhe pisace athavapi pete, ","ja510:13.2":"Kupitepi te nijjhapanam karonti; ","ja510:13.3":"Na maccuno nijjhapanam karonti, ","ja510:13.4":"Tam me mati hoti carami dhammam. ","ja510:14.1":"Aparadhake dusake hethake ca, ","ja510:14.2":"Rajano dandenti viditvana dosam; ","ja510:14.3":"Na maccuno dandayitussahanti, ","ja510:14.4":"Tam me mati hoti carami dhammam. ","ja510:15.1":"Aparadhaka dusaka hethaka ca, ","ja510:15.2":"Labhanti te rajino nijjhapetum; ","ja510:15.3":"Na maccuno nijjhapanam karonti, ","ja510:15.4":"Tam me mati hoti carami dhammam. ","ja510:16.1":"Na khattiyoti na ca brahmanoti, ","ja510:16.2":"Na addhaka balava tejavapi; ","ja510:16.3":"Na maccurajassa apekkhamatthi, ","ja510:16.4":"Tam me mati hoti carami dhammam. ","ja510:17.1":"Siha ca byaggha ca athopi dipiyo, ","ja510:17.2":"Pasayha khadanti vipphandamanam; ","ja510:17.3":"Na maccuno khaditumussahanti, ","ja510:17.4":"Tam me mati hoti carami dhammam. ","ja510:18.1":"Mayakara rangamajjhe karonta, ","ja510:18.2":"Mohenti cakkhuni janassa tavade; ","ja510:18.3":"Na maccuno mohayitussahanti, ","ja510:18.4":"Tam me mati hoti carami dhammam. ","ja510:19.1":"Asivisa kupita uggateja, ","ja510:19.2":"Damsanti marentipi te manusse; ","ja510:19.3":"Na maccuno damsitumussahanti, ","ja510:19.4":"Tam me mati hoti carami dhammam. ","ja510:20.1":"Asivisa kupita yam damsanti, ","ja510:20.2":"Tikicchaka tesa visam hananti; ","ja510:20.3":"Na maccuno datthavisam hananti, ","ja510:20.4":"Tam me mati hoti carami dhammam. ","ja510:21.1":"Dhammantari vettarani ca bhojo, ","ja510:21.2":"Visani hantvana bhujangamanam; ","ja510:21.3":"Suyyanti te kalakata tatheva, ","ja510:21.4":"Tam me mati hoti carami dhammam. ","ja510:22.1":"Vijjadhara ghoramadhiyamana, ","ja510:22.2":"Adassanam osadhehi vajanti; ","ja510:22.3":"Na maccurajassa vajantadassanam, ","ja510:22.4":"Tam me mati hoti carami dhammam. ","ja510:23.1":"Dhammo have rakkhati dhammacarim, ","ja510:23.2":"Dhammo sucinno sukhamavahati; ","ja510:23.3":"Esanisamso dhamme sucinne, ","ja510:23.4":"Na duggatim gacchati dhammacari. ","ja510:24.1":"Na hi dhammo adhammo ca, ","ja510:24.2":"Ubho samavipakino; ","ja510:24.3":"Adhammo nirayam neti, ","ja510:24.4":"Dhammo papeti suggatin”ti. ","ja510:25.1":"Ayogharajatakam cuddasamam. ","ja510:26.1":"Visatinipatam nitthitam. ","ja510:27.1":"Tassuddanam ","ja510:28.1":"Matanga sambhuta sivi sirimanto, ","ja510:28.2":"Rohana hamsa sattigumbo bhallatiya; ","ja510:28.3":"Somanassa campeyya brahma panca- ","ja510:28.4":"Pandita cirassamvata ayogharati. "}